<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="speed-v">speed <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /spiːd/    美 /spiːd/  </p>
<p>(sped / speeded, sped / speeded)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>迅速前进；超速行驶：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Delighted, I jumped into the car and speeded off.
我兴奋不已，跳上车快速开走了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police <strong>caught</strong> him <strong>speeding</strong>.
他超速行驶被警察抓住了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>快速运送：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>An ambulance sped her to the hospital.
一辆救护车迅速把她送往医院。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>加快；促进：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The best thing you can do to speed your recovery is to rest.
加快康复的最好的办法就是休息。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="speed-up">speed up</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>(使) 加快速度：</strong><br />
反 slow down </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We all need to speed up to finish in time!
我们都得加快速度以争取及时完成任务！</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 22</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Modern inventions have speeded up people’s lives amazingly.
现代发明大大加快了人们的生活节奏。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>They are broadening the bridge to speed <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the flow of traffic.  （2011 山东改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. up  </p></div>